Package: ask-cli
Version: 1.0.4
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), jq, fzf, curl
Maintainer: Ask CLI <ask-cli@example.com>
Description: AI-powered command line assistant
 Ask CLI is a command-line tool that helps you find and run
 shell commands by asking questions in natural language.
 .
 It uses OpenRouter API to get AI-powered command suggestions
 and presents them in a selectable list using fzf.
 .
 Features:
  - Ask questions in natural language to get command suggestions
  - Select commands from a list using fzf
  - View detailed explanations for each command
  - Command history with search functionality
  - Configurable API endpoint and model
